video_prompt: Woman's green eye shifts gaze. Crown reflects dappled light. Flowing hair and garment sleeves subtly ripple. Earrings sway. Background stars twinkle and cosmic streaks subtly pulse, revealing shifting astrological symbols.
image_prompt: A fair-skinned woman with flowing blonde/platinum hair wears an ornate dark crown with gems. Her striking green eye gazes right, while a textured black mask covers her nose, mouth, and chin. Dappled light illuminates her face. She wears elaborate amber and white earrings and a high-collared dark garment transitioning to purple and blue flowing sleeves. The background is a dark, star-filled cosmic sky with astrological symbols.
refined_video_prompt: Her gaze subtly shifts. Dappled light dynamically plays across the crown's surface. Hair and garment sleeves gently ripple and undulate. Earrings subtly sway. Background stars twinkle. Cosmic streaks subtly pulse, revealing and transforming astrological symbols.
